00:27:17,120 --> 00:27:19,040
It's shown that housing stability

596
00:27:19,040 --> 00:27:20,720
impacts social connections.

597
00:27:20,720 --> 00:27:23,040
City planners can implement communal areas

598
00:27:23,040 --> 00:27:24,520
for people to gather.

599
00:27:24,520 --> 00:27:27,360
A great example of this is in Barcelona, Spain.

600
00:27:28,360 --> 00:27:30,320
The American mind cannot comprehend

601
00:27:30,320 --> 00:27:31,920
what's going on around me.

602
00:27:31,920 --> 00:27:34,520
This isn't a party, it's not even a planned event.

603
00:27:34,520 --> 00:27:36,320
It's just what happens every afternoon

604
00:27:36,320 --> 00:27:38,080
here in Barcelona, Spain.

605
00:27:38,080 --> 00:27:39,320
After school and work,

606
00:27:39,320 --> 00:27:41,680
people come out to squares like this to hang out,

607
00:27:41,680 --> 00:27:43,680
get work done, whether kids play with friends,

608
00:27:43,680 --> 00:27:45,400
socialize, interact with acquaintances

609
00:27:45,400 --> 00:27:46,760
or with true friends and neighbors,

610
00:27:46,760 --> 00:27:50,000
and there's a huge social and economic benefit to that.

611
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:52,080
Now, the square I was at is right here behind me,

612
00:27:52,080 --> 00:27:55,240
but just to block away through that passageway

613
00:27:55,240 --> 00:27:56,080
is another square.

614
00:27:56,080 --> 00:27:58,000
Now, in America, we have a loneliness epidemic,

615
00:27:58,000 --> 00:28:00,400
and part of it is due to our built environment.

616
00:28:00,400 --> 00:28:02,160
You see, these public squares are example

617
00:28:02,160 --> 00:28:04,240
of what some people call third places.

618
00:28:04,240 --> 00:28:05,760
They're not work, you're first place,

619
00:28:05,760 --> 00:28:07,080
they're not home, you're second place,

620
00:28:07,080 --> 00:28:08,680
but they're a third place where you interact

621
00:28:08,680 --> 00:28:10,120
with acquaintances and friends.

622
00:28:10,120 --> 00:28:12,280
In America, these third places are dwindling

623
00:28:12,280 --> 00:28:14,800
as religion and church is having less

624
00:28:14,800 --> 00:28:17,380
of a significant impact than Americans' lives,

625
00:28:17,380 --> 00:28:19,360
but also third places are disappearing

626
00:28:19,360 --> 00:28:21,960
because of zoning laws, which keep separating

627
00:28:21,960 --> 00:28:24,880
the different types of activity that you have in a city

628
