632
00:28:35,980 --> 00:28:38,520
for people who are poor, at least on a regular basis.

633
00:28:38,520 --> 00:28:40,320
Now, why does it happen here in Spain?

634
00:28:40,320 --> 00:28:42,360
Well, of course, there's a culture for it,

635
00:28:42,360 --> 00:28:44,080
but more than that, there's an environment

636
