your wellbeing.

722
00:32:33,120 --> 00:32:36,560
Dr. Noble also advises to choose social media platforms

723
00:32:36,560 --> 00:32:40,040
that help us develop authentic social connections.

724
00:32:40,040 --> 00:32:43,000
Number five, giving to others.

725
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:45,160
Giving to others shows us that we have something

726
00:32:45,160 --> 00:32:46,400
to offer to the world.

727
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:49,200
Ironically, this can help us feel less lonely,

728
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:50,840
local community volunteering,

729
00:32:50,840 --> 00:32:54,720
or just helping a work colleague or neighbor in small ways.

