737
00:33:10,240 --> 00:33:13,120
And lastly, number six, connection.

738
00:33:13,120 --> 00:33:14,880
Loneliness is a stress state

739
00:33:14,880 --> 00:33:16,480
that makes us focus on ourselves

740
00:33:16,480 --> 00:33:19,080
rather than outwards towards others.

741
00:33:19,080 --> 00:33:22,200
To keep safe, we often treat people and things

742
00:33:22,200 --> 00:33:24,520
with suspicion when we feel lonely.

743
00:33:24,520 --> 00:33:26,040
This can ruin self-esteem.

744
00:33:26,040 --> 00:33:28,640
We feel like we're not lovable or likeable.

745
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:30,640
These factors compound on each other,

746
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:33,920
making it hard to solve and creating a downward spiral.

747
00:33:33,920 --> 00:33:36,440
To break the cycle, one can start slowly.

748
00:33:36,440 --> 00:33:38,160
Even a quick hello to your neighbors

749
00:33:38,160 --> 00:33:40,560
